{"tid":844263,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【曼聯風波】內幕料！費Sir贊成清洗普巴","createTime":"2018-10-01T17:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T05:07:31.000Z","uid":1426,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"152562ddffba56e4a7fc9e025921f0799d7dab8a","tid":844263,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"傳聞費格遜(右)支持莫連奴清洗保羅普巴。(Getty Images)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181001/photo/bkn-20181001160321697-1001_00882_001_01p.jpg?20181001160350\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181001160321697-1001_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20181001160350&h=006270fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》大爆，曼聯領隊莫連奴同保羅普巴嘅不和傳聞，已經引起紅魔傳奇領隊費格遜不滿，消息話費爵爺支持清洗保羅普巴，甚至可能會出手干涉趕佢扯！<br />\n<br />\n據講費格遜同卜比查爾頓認為，曼聯所有更衣室問題都應該內部解決，絕對唔可以每日喺網上連載，仲話情況惡化落去，佢哋可能會聯手作出干涉，支持莫連奴清洗保羅普巴，報道仲提到費爵爺曾經喺自傳中，承認自己好唔鍾意呢個人。<br />\n<br />\n2012年保羅普巴離開曼聯曼聯轉投祖雲達斯，開始踏上頂級球星之路，但費格遜喺自傳中強調，完全冇後悔過當年放佢走：「我好慶幸普巴當時離隊，我唔需要佢呢種球員，如果佢係我嘅球員，佢唔會有出場機會。」"},{"pid":"e9f6cea5e948eeae434ae2996c4046bd8687971b","tid":844263,"uid":8932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"點解費老會咁憎普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538959c3795e212b2b3786154aeb0da12903a490","tid":844263,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"普巴朋友隊冇左普巴會得翻幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bebd3801daa2a2a5ebd37b7cbc9a7def375a72","tid":844263,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9f6cea5e948eeae434ae2996c4046bd8687971b","tid":844263,"uid":8932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"點解費老會咁憎普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma